welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Garching bei Munchen, a charming city known for its beautiful parks and lively culture. We hope you enjoy your stay and take the time to explore all that this wonderful city has to offer. Have a great time!"

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal of Franz Josef Strauss Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: A newer terminal primarily used for Lufthansa flights and other Star Alliance airlines.

terminals.name: Terminal 3
terminals.description: A smaller terminal used for low-cost carriers and some regional flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport, but a premium option is also available for faster speeds.
